664
00:59:17,666 --> 00:59:22,832
The division of local services is a state body that helps cities and towns be financially responsible.

665
00:59:23,331 --> 00:59:30,478
It recommends cities and towns have between three and 5% of their total budget and free cash every year to maintain a good bond rating.

666
00:59:30,979 --> 00:59:34,422
